雖然國家名稱是"英國", [[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]]有權成為為英國代表團的一部分。[[Northern_Ireland_Executive|北愛爾蘭政府]]的代表，然而，他們反對這個名字，他們認為這個名字造成了北愛爾蘭不是英國奧運隊伍的一部分，並呼籲該隊改名為Team UK。<ref>"No place for 'NI', says Olympic Team GB", Belfast Telegraph, 10 March 2011</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Minister urges BOA to change 'erroneous Team GB name'|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-northern-ireland-12688705|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=27 April 2011|date=10 March 2011|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041102/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-northern-ireland-12688705|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根據[[英國奧林匹克委員會|英國奧林匹克委員會]]與[[愛爾蘭奧林匹克議會|愛爾蘭奧林匹克議會]]的長期協議，[[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]]的運動員可以代表[[奥林匹克运动会爱尔兰代表团|愛爾蘭奧運隊]]參賽，因為[[北愛爾蘭人|北愛爾蘭人]]理論上擁有[[多重国籍|多重国籍]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Full text of the constitution |publisher=[http://www.taoiseach.gov.ie/ Department of the Taoiseach] |url=http://www.taoiseach.gov.ie/attached_files/Pdf%20files/Constitution%20of%20Ireland.pdf |accessdate=2010-02-17 |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20050415121010/http://www.taoiseach.gov.ie/attached_files/Pdf%20files/Constitution%20of%20Ireland.pdf |archivedate=2005-04-15 }}</ref>

英國最成功的帕運選手是游泳的[[Mike_Kenny_(swimmer)|Mike Kenny]]在參與四屆帕運會中獲得16面個人金牌及兩面接力銀牌。<ref name="PC">{{cite web|url=http://www.paralympiansclub.org.uk/athlete.asp?itemid=50&itemTitle=Mike+Kenny&section=70&sectionTitle=Search+For+An+Athlete&games=&sport=&medal_gold=&medal_silver=&medal_bronze=&keyword=mike%20kenny|title=Mike Kenny (swimmer)|publisher=Paralympians' Club|accessdate=29 August 2012}}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>雖然英國參加了每屆帕運會但是直到1989年在Kenny退役以後才成立[[英國帕拉林匹克委員會|英國帕拉林匹克委員會]]。 
來自英國的傳媒不斷提及那年參與殘奧會最多的運動員， [[譚妮·葛雷-湯普森|譚妮·葛雷-湯普森]]、[[David_Roberts_(swimmer)|Dave Roberts]] and [[Sarah_Storey|Sarah Storey]] 被稱為英國“最偉大的殘奧運動員”，偶爾用“現代”這個詞。<ref>{{cite web |title=Sarah Storey Britain's greatest Paralympian of the modern era |publisher=[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/ Daily Telegraph] |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/paralympic-sport/9525433/Sarah-Storeys-11th-gold-medal-makes-her-Great-Britains-greatest-Paralympian-of-the-modern-era.html |accessdate=2012-10-12 |archive-date=2015-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926041633/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/paralympic-sport/9525433/Sarah-Storeys-11th-gold-medal-makes-her-Great-Britains-greatest-Paralympian-of-the-modern-era.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，國際殘奧委員會將所有kenny的十八面獎牌都認定為殘奧獎牌<ref>{{cite web |title=Meet Britain's other greatest Paralympian |publisher=[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/ Daily Telegraph] |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/paralympic-sport/paralympics-gb/9520247/Meet-Britains-other-greatest-Paralympian.html |accessdate=2012-02-17 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234445/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/paralympic-sport/paralympics-gb/9520247/Meet-Britains-other-greatest-Paralympian.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

英國首面帕運金牌為[[Margaret_Maughan|Margaret Maughan]]在[[1960年夏季残奥会|1960年夏季残奥会]]獲得。<ref name="OBS-IPC1-OC">Olympic Broadcasting Service, channel IPC1, Paralympics International Feed, "2012 Summer Paralympics Opening Ceremonies", airdate 29 August 2012</ref>

英國首面冬季帕運金牌為[[Kelly_Gallagher_(alpine_skier)|Kelly Gallagher]]與其導航者[[Charlotte_Evans|Charlotte Evans]]在[[2014年冬季帕拉林匹克運動會|2014年冬季帕拉林匹克運動會]]在[[Alpine_skiing_at_the_2014_Winter_Paralympics –_Women's_downhill|女子超級大彎道]]視覺障礙項目獲得。
